ric is a Fortune global 500 company. To learn more about Sumitomo Electric Group, please visit http://global-sei.com.','http://www.juddwire.com/','https://cdn.builtin.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,fit=contain,w=200,h=200,q=100/https://builtin.com/sites/www.builtin.com/files/2022-11/Judd Wire, Inc..jpg'),(2279,'New England Sports Network',NULL,'https://nesn.com/','https://cdn.builtin.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,fit=contain,w=200,h=200,q=100/https://builtin.com/sites/www.builtin.com/files/2022-09/New England Sports Network.jpg'),(2280,'Burns & McDonnell','We are a family of companies with an unmatched team of 10,000 engineers, construction professionals, architects, technologists, scientists and consultants with offices across the U.S. and throughout the world. Our singular mission since 1898 has been to make our clients successful. When we plan, design, permit, construct and manage projects worldwide, we do it like we own it. As a 100% employee-owned firm ranking in the top leading firms for safety, each professional brings an ownership mentality to our projects. That means we think like owners, working through each challenge until it’s resolved, exceeding our clients’ goals.','http://www.burnsmcd.com/','https://cdn.builtin.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,fit=contain,w=200,h=200,q=100/https://builtin.com/sites/www.builtin.com/files/2022-04/Burns & McDonnell .jpeg'),(2281,'SHOES.COM','Our mission is to help every person find the best shoes for their journey through easy, accessible, expert-guided shopping. Shoes.com is headquartered in the greatest shoe city in the world - Boston, Massachusetts, the birthplace of American shoe manufacturing. In 1999, we founded the first online shoe shopping destination. Over the past two decades, we’ve served millions of shoe-adoring customers of all shapes, sizes, and tastes. We are obsessed with helping our customers find that perfect pair. And each day we are one step closer to delivering smarter, personalized shoe-shopping, at great value. We’r