enge. We think strategically but are not afraid to roll-up our sleeves and get the job done no matter how big or small. We are dedicated and focused, but also make time to play and celebrate our successes. • Authentic – we are a diverse team with a wide range of backgrounds and skills that genuinely like each other and the work that we do • Dedicated – we are supportive of each other and our customers with the goal of changing the face of security imaging • Industrious – we’re continually working to improve the customer experience and bring out the best in each other • Aware – we know what’s at stake and how our customers are counting on us to help keep them safe each and every day RaySecur has transformed how leading security teams keep their people and business safe from all types of mail attacks.','https://raysecur.com/','https://cdn.builtin.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,fit=contain,w=200,h=200,q=100/https://builtin.com/sites/www.builtin.com/files/2023-05/RaySecur Inc.jpeg'),(2754,'Valo Health','Valo is a technology company built to transform the drug discovery and development process using human-centric data and AI-powered computation. Valo is fully integrating human-centric data across the entire drug development lifecycle into a single unified architecture, thereby accelerating the discovery and development of life-changing drugs while simultaneously reducing the cost, time, and failure rate. The company’s Opal Computational Platform™ consists of an integrated set of capabilities designed to transform data into valuable insights that may accelerate discoveries and enable Valo to advance a robust pipeline of programs across cardiovascular metabolic renal, oncology, and neurodegenerative disease.','http://www.valohealth.com/','https://cdn.builtin.com/cdn-cgi/image/f=auto,fit=contain,w=200,h=200,q=100/https://builtin.com/sites/www.builtin.com/files/2022-10/309FEFCC-35C0-4CD9-9D25-6201D0ED3897.jpeg'),(2755,'Tripadvisor','Tripadvisor, the world\'s largest travel guidanc